title: SHANY Cosmetics SHANY Masquerade Eyeliner Gel Color Smudge Proof Set, 12 count
description: The Shany gel eyeliner set comes with 12 different colored gel eyeliners in individual containers. Each container is securely fastened with a screw on lid and the jars can be taken separately in a group, so you can travel as lightly as you need. This eyeliner set has gorgeous and versatile colors and might just be the last eyeliners you have to buy...until you run out. Made with materials imported from Luxembourg and Paris, these liners go on smooth and stay on for hours, a result of the high quality ingredients used in production.

title: SHANY Cosmetics Eyelash Extend Assorted Reusable Eyelashes Thick and Dramatic, 3.6 Ounce
description: Make a statement with your eyes. Don't stop with gorgeous Shany eye shadows to add glamour to your look. Top off fantastically colored eyes with these super chic false eyelashes.
